items.title: Simpler approach pays off for Darvish
items.summary: Until he put the brakes to a poorly timed slump with seven scoreless innings in Wednesday night's 4-1 win over the Giants, even Darvish conceded he was running out of time to show the Dodgers he can be counted on to fill that role.
